{"tid":2189012,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"巫師3將會推出次世代高畫質版本","createTime":"2020-09-04T14:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T10:45:58.000Z","uid":159183,"like":96,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"d2507cd99f95871dbc520cb87d6c76238ecd1c98","tid":2189012,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:57:12.000Z","msg":"CD Projekt Red 稍早前宣布旗下全球暢銷大作《巫師 3：狂獵》（The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt）為迎接今年即將到來的次世代主機 PS5、Xbox Series X 到來，遊戲推出全面「高畫質完全版」，而已在 PS4、Xbox One 以及 PC 平台擁有遊戲的玩家，將可免費獲得升級更新。<br />\n根據官方公告，全新高畫質版本將會在 PS5、Xbox Series X 獨立販售推出，內容將包含《石之心》、《血與酒》等 DLC 內容，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">而最重要的是之其在舊平台已購買遊戲的玩家，將可免費升級遊戲至高畫質版</span></span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6mxfLtx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6mxfLtx.jpg&h=832e5559&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cbda9b1d50619b54ea86b0095c7595b600e6485","tid":2189012,"uid":107927,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"良心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa174dacd16cadfe1aaece01df259c6dc9e902f8","tid":2189012,"uid":74970,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"終於有原本trailer既畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7afc7304077be124b3fe39ad4cd945f15bd0a578","tid":2189012,"uid":11914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fa174dacd16cadfe1aaece01df259c6dc9e902f8","tid":2189012,"uid":74970,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"終於有原本trailer既畫質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"唔會啦 最多都係pc 版maximum setting"},{"pid":"23d712007d09cb9f27da5c462da10cf08218a3a4","tid":2189012,"uid":74970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7afc7304077be124b3fe39ad4cd945f15bd0a578","tid":2189012,"uid":11914,"like":1,"di